Name: Insight
About the game: Draw lines, and divide a large shape into small shapes. You need to observe what kind of parts the whole is composed of. Various symbols are waiting for you to explore. Feature -There is no tutorial, the level itself is a tutorial. -Conciseness is maintained. -Occasional brain teasers. -A total of 49 different level areas, each level area has a unique variant or new mechanism.
